  <brief_title>Association Study of Gene Polymorphisms With Cardiac Performance</brief_title>
  <official_title>Observational Association Study of G Protein Polymorphisms With Cardiac Performance in Coronary Artery Disease Patients Undergoing Coronary Artery Bypass Grafting</official_title>
